                                                                                  // the filter RAM has a size of 4096 elements
                                                                                  // each element has a size of 4 bytes
                                                                                  // (definition of filter bits: see below)
                                                                                  // the filter RAM is addressed in the following way
                                                                                  //    uint32_t *pFilter; 
